## **Risk Mitigations**

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| Data availability | Use synthetic data generator (no PHI liability) |
| HIPAA/regulatory | Stay in "educational" scope; no real patient data; add BAA disclaimers |
| Model training time | Use small datasets; pre-train on public cohorts if needed |
| LLM cost | Use free-tier API (Claude dev sandbox) or local Ollama |
| Scope creep | Strictly MVP: 1 chronic condition (HTN+diabetes overlap), 3–4 alert types |

